1
00:00:05,990 --> 00:00:08,685
♫  I want to go to the future  ♫

2
00:00:08,685 --> 00:00:12,140
♫  Time bears witness to my quirkiness  ♫

3
00:00:12,140 --> 00:00:18,233
♫  I want to seize the day and put the whole world into my head  ♫

4
00:00:18,233 --> 00:00:24,459
♫  I want to go back in time to do all the crazy things I didn't do  ♫

5
00:00:24,459 --> 00:00:30,580
♫  Don't say goodbye, don't be in a daze, let my radiant light be bright  ♫

6
00:00:30,580 --> 00:00:36,066
♫  We are always looking forward to the unknown future  ♫

7
00:00:36,066 --> 00:00:43,166
♫  And often overlooking our surroundings and best plan in front of us  ♫

8
00:00:43,166 --> 00:00:48,390
♫  Every day my heart beats for you  ♫

9
00:00:48,390 --> 00:00:49,903
♫  Be your light  ♫

10
00:00:49,903 --> 00:00:55,566
♫  You are no doubt irreplaceable  ♫

11
00:00:55,566 --> 00:01:02,166
♫  Every day the sun shines through the window  ♫

12
00:01:02,166 --> 00:01:08,733
♫  With your reflection being my incredible highlight  ♫

13
00:01:08,733 --> 00:01:11,730
[I Don't Want to be Brothers with You]

14
00:01:12,460 --> 00:01:14,079
All right.

15
00:01:14,079 --> 00:01:17,660
Well, you have the final exam papers in your hands.

16
00:01:17,660 --> 00:01:18,940
Take a good look at them.

17
00:01:18,940 --> 00:01:22,059
Through this exam, I was able to see your spirit.

18
00:01:22,059 --> 00:01:25,499
A few students in our class have made great progress with their grades.

19
00:01:25,499 --> 00:01:29,119
As your teacher, I'm very proud of you. Let's give yourselves a round of applause.

20
00:01:32,640 --> 00:01:34,779
Take him as an example. Don't be complacent.

21
00:01:34,779 --> 00:01:37,820
Although the overall situation is satisfactory,

22
00:01:37,820 --> 00:01:42,900
some students are still going against this general trend in terms of their grades.

23
00:01:42,900 --> 00:01:46,900
I won't call any names. You should know what I'm talking about.

24
00:01:46,900 --> 00:01:49,840
You will not be children after the summer vacation. You'll be seniors.

25
00:01:49,840 --> 00:01:54,740
I hope everyone can really think about their future during this summer vacation, okay?

26
00:01:54,740 --> 00:01:57,319
Don't just focus on playing, okay?

27
00:01:57,319 --> 00:01:58,919
Class dismissed.

28
00:02:04,850 --> 00:02:08,139
Xiaowen, you're going to the library again?

29
00:02:16,530 --> 00:02:20,100
Oh, God. Your scores are terrible. You failed all your subjects.

30
00:02:21,059 --> 00:02:23,920
Don't talk about me. How did you do on the exam?

31
00:02:26,770 --> 00:02:31,059
I think I can get new headphones this time.

32
00:02:31,059 --> 00:02:34,740
You can have these. Good luck.

33
00:02:56,530 --> 00:02:59,639
Gao Yang is such a big fat liar.

34
00:02:59,639 --> 00:03:02,659
He said he'd change the scores on my exam.

35
00:03:02,659 --> 00:03:07,779
What did he do? I still failed.

36
00:03:09,090 --> 00:03:12,379
Beibei, I really want to comfort you,

37
00:03:12,379 --> 00:03:16,539
but honestly, I didn't do very well on the exam.

38
00:03:18,420 --> 00:03:21,019
You didn't do very well?

39
00:03:21,019 --> 00:03:24,140
I got the same ranking as last time.

40
00:03:24,619 --> 00:03:27,740
No progress means regress.

41
00:03:29,019 --> 00:03:31,399
I can't go out during the summer vacation.

42
00:03:33,439 --> 00:03:37,580
Meng, who's going to keep me company then?

43
00:03:38,020 --> 00:03:40,099
It's all right.

44
00:03:44,860 --> 00:03:46,360
Beibei,

45
00:03:47,150 --> 00:03:49,379
I... I...

46
00:03:49,379 --> 00:03:51,980
Are you here to mock me?

47
00:03:51,980 --> 00:03:56,319
Jia, are you going to the boot camp soon?

48
00:03:56,860 --> 00:03:58,059
Tomorrow.

49
00:03:58,059 --> 00:04:00,339
You're leaving tomorrow?

50
00:04:09,980 --> 00:04:12,880
Beibei,

51
00:04:12,880 --> 00:04:17,039
actually, I've been trying to

52
00:04:17,039 --> 00:04:19,479
find a chance

53
00:04:19,479 --> 00:04:21,780
to apologize to you.

54
00:04:22,539 --> 00:04:24,339
I'm sorry.

55
00:04:25,179 --> 00:04:30,260
I only said that in the heat of the moment. I really want to watch the show.

56
00:04:30,260 --> 00:04:33,260
I-I really want to thank you.

57
00:04:34,319 --> 00:04:39,620
But... Mi Jia, with my terrible grades,

58
00:04:39,620 --> 00:04:44,220
I won't be able to get signatures for you.

59
00:04:45,980 --> 00:04:50,500
No, no... I-I-It's all my fault.

60
00:04:50,500 --> 00:04:55,499
Y-You... I-I was the one who told them that you cheated on the exam.

61
00:04:57,580 --> 00:05:00,119
Why, Jia?

62
00:05:00,119 --> 00:05:02,639
I-I-I didn't do it on purpose.

63
00:05:02,639 --> 00:05:04,299
I-I'm sorry. I really didn't do it on purpose.

64
00:05:04,299 --> 00:05:07,879
I-I didn't know what you were doing at the time.

65
00:05:07,879 --> 00:05:11,839
P-Please forgive me. I really didn't do it on purpose, Beibei.

66
00:05:12,659 --> 00:05:14,639
No.

67
00:05:14,639 --> 00:05:21,099
If I had better grades, if I could be smarter, none of this would happen.

68
00:05:21,099 --> 00:05:24,839
I would be able to get signatures for you.

69
00:05:24,839 --> 00:05:26,539
No...

70
00:05:26,539 --> 00:05:30,339
I will never cheat again!

71
00:05:30,339 --> 00:05:33,680
I'll never fight with you again, Beibei!

72
00:05:33,680 --> 00:05:37,900
Jia, I missed you so much!

73
00:05:39,070 --> 00:05:43,740
Stop crying.

74
00:05:49,850 --> 00:05:51,240
Xiaowen,

75
00:05:51,240 --> 00:05:56,040
I don't know what to say. Your grades are as good as always.

76
00:05:56,040 --> 00:05:58,419
Keep up the good work.

77
00:06:03,970 --> 00:06:05,060
What are you doing?

78
00:06:05,060 --> 00:06:07,740
I didn't do well on the exam. I accept your punishment.

79
00:06:08,240 --> 00:06:10,620
How old are you now? Why are you still playing with weapons?

80
00:06:10,620 --> 00:06:12,659
Even if you can stand it, do I have the strength to wave that?

81
00:06:12,659 --> 00:06:15,020
I won't talk about your problems today. Go get some rest.

82
00:06:15,020 --> 00:06:16,620
Copy.

83
00:06:17,700 --> 00:06:22,579
Xiaowen, I have some good news for you today.

84
00:06:23,460 --> 00:06:28,900
Well, I got drunk and delayed your training.

85
00:06:28,900 --> 00:06:30,939
I want to apologize to you.

86
00:06:31,620 --> 00:06:33,859
That's all right, Mr. Gao.

87
00:06:35,140 --> 00:06:40,239
- I'm going back to the room.
- Wait a minute. I haven't told you the good news yet.

88
00:06:43,630 --> 00:06:45,079
I've considered it carefully.

89
00:06:45,779 --> 00:06:51,179
I'm indeed not very reliable sometimes. It makes sense that you don't trust me.

90
00:06:51,179 --> 00:06:54,139
However, you can't put off your training.

91
00:06:54,139 --> 00:06:56,400
You need someone to guide you.

92
00:06:56,400 --> 00:06:59,419
You can go to the provincial boot camp the day after tomorrow.

93
00:06:59,419 --> 00:07:01,400
The provincial boot camp?

94
00:07:02,290 --> 00:07:05,059
I didn't get a score during the last competition.

95
00:07:05,620 --> 00:07:08,299
The coach of the provincial team is my college alumni.

96
00:07:08,299 --> 00:07:13,799
I told you about your situation. He said he noticed you a long time ago.

97
00:07:14,339 --> 00:07:18,899
You have the skills to be the champion.

98
00:07:18,899 --> 00:07:23,639
So, is that why you drank so much last time?

99
00:07:24,659 --> 00:07:26,500
Let's forget about the past.

100
00:07:26,500 --> 00:07:29,419
- Mr. Gao...
- Don't thank me.

101
00:07:29,940 --> 00:07:34,020
He really likes you. It's because of your own abilities.

102
00:07:34,020 --> 00:07:35,500
All right, Xiaowen.

103
00:07:35,500 --> 00:07:40,340
Go back to the room and pack up. I won't help you pack up.

104
00:07:40,340 --> 00:07:44,180
Thank you, Mr. Gao.

105
00:08:12,417 --> 00:08:18,003
[Episode 19: An Unconventional Summer Vacation]

106
00:08:24,079 --> 00:08:25,779
Are you asleep?

107
00:08:26,940 --> 00:08:31,559
Well, I'll send you off tomorrow.

108
00:08:35,290 --> 00:08:39,840
Gao Bin is alright. He's useful after all.

109
00:08:43,450 --> 00:08:46,560
What have you been working on lately?

110
00:08:46,560 --> 00:08:51,160
The final exams are over. Why are you still going to the library?

111
00:08:58,340 --> 00:09:00,659
You're asleep?

112
00:09:00,659 --> 00:09:02,359
Goodnight.

113
00:09:09,939 --> 00:09:11,980
Goodnight.

114
00:09:32,690 --> 00:09:35,599
Xiaowen. Xiaowen!

115
00:09:35,599 --> 00:09:38,739
What are you yelling for? Xiaowen left a long time ago.

116
00:09:41,220 --> 00:09:43,579
Why didn't he tell me?

117
00:10:00,090 --> 00:10:01,850
[5 Years of High School in 3 Years]

118
00:10:09,910 --> 00:10:14,590
[Middle School Workbook]

119
00:10:19,140 --> 00:10:21,910
[Explanation of "Lanting"]

120
00:10:32,180 --> 00:10:37,020
[As I said last time, "No way."]

121
00:11:03,480 --> 00:11:05,179
Welcome to the Provincial Team's Boot camp.

122
00:11:05,179 --> 00:11:08,260
You are all seedlings carefully chosen within the province.

123
00:11:08,260 --> 00:11:12,579
In the upcoming month, I hope everyone will train hard,

124
00:11:12,579 --> 00:11:15,539
get along with each other, and benefit from the boot camp.

125
00:11:15,539 --> 00:11:17,900
You two, pass out the training uniforms.

126
00:11:17,900 --> 00:11:19,300
Okay.

127
00:11:24,380 --> 00:11:27,000
Pass these six uniforms down.

128
00:11:34,810 --> 00:11:37,359
Coach, that's not right. We're missing one. I don't have one.

129
00:11:37,359 --> 00:11:39,040
We're missing one?

130
00:11:40,260 --> 00:11:41,760
I don't have one.

131
00:11:46,020 --> 00:11:51,159
Ye Xiaowen, give the uniform to Sizhe. Yours hasn't arrived yet.

132
00:12:06,290 --> 00:12:09,879
Change into your uniforms and train in groups. Break it up.

133
00:12:09,879 --> 00:12:11,219
Okay.

134
00:12:16,900 --> 00:12:22,700
Gao Yang, we're so sad. We have to study at home during the summer vacation.

135
00:12:22,700 --> 00:12:29,040
Jia and Xiaowen are not here. Meng can't come out either. I'm so bored.

136
00:12:29,040 --> 00:12:30,140
What did you say?

137
00:12:30,140 --> 00:12:32,059
Are you listening to me?

138
00:12:32,059 --> 00:12:35,120
I am. That's because we both made mistakes.

139
00:12:35,120 --> 00:12:39,460
Xiaowen left me a few exercise books. I have to finish them soon to atone for my sins.

140
00:12:39,460 --> 00:12:41,559
Beibei, did you finish your homework?

141
00:12:41,559 --> 00:12:45,459
Watermelon, w-a-t-e-r...

142
00:12:49,500 --> 00:12:54,080
Xiaowen, what does A square times B square mean?

143
00:13:08,690 --> 00:13:12,599
Put some force in it. Stretch your muscles.

144
00:13:18,220 --> 00:13:20,460
How did you get in here?

145
00:13:23,380 --> 00:13:28,680
Do you remember me? I'm the champion of the Tieyuan Long-Distance Race.

146
00:13:32,900 --> 00:13:34,699
You're an interesting fellow.

147
00:13:34,699 --> 00:13:39,039
You gave up during the race and now you pulled strings to get in. What are you thinking?

148
00:13:39,039 --> 00:13:41,179
None of your business.

149
00:13:43,690 --> 00:13:47,820
Why are you so arrogant? You can't defeat me no matter how hard you train.

150
00:13:58,960 --> 00:14:01,300
Gao Yang, time for lunch.

151
00:14:01,300 --> 00:14:06,500
I have a teacher at home but you teach PE. I can't ask you anything.

152
00:14:06,500 --> 00:14:09,220
Why are you blaming me if you don't know how to solve a problem?

153
00:14:09,220 --> 00:14:12,659
Now you know the importance of Xiaowen. You used to bully him all the time.

154
00:14:12,659 --> 00:14:15,220
I'm asking you one more time. Are you eating lunch or not?

155
00:14:15,220 --> 00:14:19,200
No. I'm not in the mood to eat if I don't finish these problems.

156
00:14:19,200 --> 00:14:21,500
Fine, a man of integrity.

157
00:14:28,170 --> 00:14:31,020
Hurry up. Go clean yourself up.

158
00:14:33,120 --> 00:14:34,680
Xiaowen,

159
00:14:34,680 --> 00:14:39,240
did the coach tell you when you'll get your uniform?

160
00:14:39,240 --> 00:14:40,860
What's the matter?

161
00:14:42,860 --> 00:14:44,939
Did anyone say anything?

162
00:14:45,650 --> 00:14:46,860
No.

163
00:14:46,860 --> 00:14:52,819
It's just... some people said... you came in through connections.

164
00:14:57,500 --> 00:15:02,540
Don't mind them. I did come in because Mr. Gao pulled some strings.

165
00:15:03,350 --> 00:15:06,470
But if I can run faster than them,

166
00:15:06,470 --> 00:15:10,220
they won't say anything anymore, right?

167
00:15:13,810 --> 00:15:15,419
All right,

168
00:15:16,220 --> 00:15:19,500
then don't... don't take it to heart.

169
00:15:20,110 --> 00:15:23,380
I-I'll go back to the dorms now.

170
00:15:24,030 --> 00:15:26,440
You should go back soon too.

171
00:15:26,440 --> 00:15:28,080
Don't worry.

172
00:15:45,620 --> 00:15:47,320
I'm sorry.

173
00:15:53,130 --> 00:15:57,900
Sizhe, would he tell the coach on us?

174
00:15:57,900 --> 00:15:59,739
He wouldn't dare.

175
00:16:07,900 --> 00:16:12,419
I'm sneaking out for a while. You should know what to do.

176
00:16:12,419 --> 00:16:15,740
I don't care what you guys do.

177
00:16:15,740 --> 00:16:18,499
Fine, keep your mouth shut.

178
00:16:19,100 --> 00:16:21,260
How about it? Are you ready?

179
00:16:21,260 --> 00:16:22,760
Yes.

180
00:16:37,570 --> 00:16:39,880
Hello, who are you looking for?

181
00:16:43,740 --> 00:16:47,459
Hello? Who is it? Say something.

182
00:16:51,860 --> 00:16:56,320
Who is that? Is he crazy?

183
00:17:09,300 --> 00:17:11,259
Gao Yang, it's your turn.

184
00:17:11,259 --> 00:17:13,559
I'm solving a problem.

185
00:17:13,559 --> 00:17:15,760
They charge by the hour here.

186
00:17:15,760 --> 00:17:21,459
How many seconds would I waste? Trying to save up again? What are you saving money for? Another competition?

187
00:17:21,459 --> 00:17:23,179
I want to buy headphones.

188
00:17:23,179 --> 00:17:28,020
Why do you want to buy headphones again? You have so many headphones already. You want to open a headphone store?

189
00:17:28,020 --> 00:17:30,019
Don't worry about it.

190
00:17:33,150 --> 00:17:38,100
Gao Yang, you should just... answer them casually.

191
00:17:38,100 --> 00:17:42,940
Do you remember how we handled vacation homework when we went to school together?

192
00:17:42,940 --> 00:17:47,280
With one pen, one person, in one night,

193
00:17:48,410 --> 00:17:50,839
we created a miracle.

194
00:17:50,839 --> 00:17:55,599
You think I don't want to? Xiaowen will surely check it. I have to finish it soon.

195
00:17:55,599 --> 00:17:58,419
I get so sleepy if I do it at home.

196
00:17:59,060 --> 00:18:02,580
Wait, what's going on? Am I your reading partner?

197
00:18:05,790 --> 00:18:08,799
I won! Loser buys the drinks.

198
00:18:08,799 --> 00:18:10,259
What do you mean you won?

199
00:18:10,259 --> 00:18:11,759
I cleared the table with one shot. You've never seen that before?

200
00:18:11,759 --> 00:18:15,899
Clear the table with one shot? You cleared the table with one shot? That's less than one minute. Do you think you're O'Sullivan?

201
00:18:15,899 --> 00:18:20,219
Hurry up. Don't blame me if you don't focus on the game. Go buy the drinks.

202
00:18:20,219 --> 00:18:23,179
Hey, time to set the table. Bring us two more drinks.

203
00:18:23,179 --> 00:18:25,659
Set the table! Hurry up!

204
00:18:26,240 --> 00:18:27,940
Coming, Bro.

205
00:18:31,540 --> 00:18:33,140
I'm sorry.

206
00:18:42,340 --> 00:18:44,140
Dawei.

207
00:18:50,450 --> 00:18:51,820
Why are you here?

208
00:18:51,820 --> 00:18:56,139
You're climbing over the wall every day. Is the outside world that interesting?

209
00:18:56,139 --> 00:18:59,400
Do you have any self-discipline as an athlete?

210
00:18:59,400 --> 00:19:02,399
Coach, we just went out once.

211
00:19:02,399 --> 00:19:07,319
Once? Just once? You did that several times last week!

212
00:19:07,319 --> 00:19:08,900
You think I don't know?

213
00:19:08,900 --> 00:19:10,600
Coach.

214
00:19:12,650 --> 00:19:14,459
What are you looking at?

215
00:19:15,410 --> 00:19:20,360
Let me tell you again. If you don't want to train, many other athletes want to get in.

216
00:19:20,360 --> 00:19:22,839
If you don't cherish this, a lot of people will!

217
00:19:22,839 --> 00:19:25,100
Listen carefully,

218
00:19:25,100 --> 00:19:30,820
if you violate any discipline again, you will be dismissed immediately!

219
00:19:33,060 --> 00:19:36,500
Go, do fifty laps on the field.

220
00:19:40,690 --> 00:19:42,499
Go now!

221
00:19:48,930 --> 00:19:50,340
How's it going? Are you adapting all right?

222
00:19:50,340 --> 00:19:52,259
I'm adapting quite well, Coach.

223
00:19:52,259 --> 00:19:55,739
Okay, let me know if there's a problem at any time.

224
00:20:08,400 --> 00:20:11,220
Bro, your turn.

225
00:20:13,060 --> 00:20:16,959
Dawei, why did you get a job?

226
00:20:18,659 --> 00:20:20,980
None of your business.

227
00:20:20,980 --> 00:20:24,679
From the look of this, are you planning to start working?

228
00:20:24,679 --> 00:20:26,500
You didn't do well on the exam, right?

229
00:20:27,140 --> 00:20:30,020
Shut up. The scores aren't published yet.

230
00:20:30,020 --> 00:20:32,860
Well, I wish you a great future and splendid prospects.

231
00:20:32,860 --> 00:20:36,780
I wish you will go to college in Ha in an. Don't let me see you again.

232
00:20:40,100 --> 00:20:43,300
What are you writing on those pages?

233
00:20:43,300 --> 00:20:45,160
This is the homework Xiaowen left me.

234
00:20:45,160 --> 00:20:48,059
Xiaowen? Where is he?

235
00:20:48,059 --> 00:20:51,760
Aren't you guys inseparable?

236
00:20:53,219 --> 00:20:55,540
He went to the provincial boot camp.

237
00:20:55,540 --> 00:21:00,520
The next time you see Xiaowen, it will be at the arena of the Olympic Games.

238
00:21:01,019 --> 00:21:02,619
Him?

239
00:21:02,979 --> 00:21:06,419
He'll surely take a beating in the boot camp.

240
00:21:06,419 --> 00:21:07,300
What do you mean?

241
00:21:07,300 --> 00:21:09,700
Athletes are pretty simple.

242
00:21:09,700 --> 00:21:12,359
He likes to keep to himself.

243
00:21:13,279 --> 00:21:15,879
They would certainly think he's pompous.

244
00:21:15,880 --> 00:21:20,660
That... that's because they don't know him. Xiaowen isn't like that.

245
00:21:20,660 --> 00:21:23,940
Not all athletes are as good-natured as I am.

246
00:21:23,940 --> 00:21:26,380
Yeah, right. You're good-natured?

247
00:21:26,380 --> 00:21:29,699
Those are elite athletes from all over the province, okay?

248
00:21:29,699 --> 00:21:32,540
They are very well-behaved. Do you think they're like you?

249
00:21:32,540 --> 00:21:34,440
Don't believe me then.

250
00:21:36,140 --> 00:21:37,699
Go ahead.

251
00:21:37,699 --> 00:21:40,419
Bro, what pattern is mine?

252
00:21:40,419 --> 00:21:42,019
The solids.

253
00:21:42,508 --> 00:21:44,308
Okay.

254
00:21:47,100 --> 00:21:49,300
Did you tell on us?

255
00:21:49,300 --> 00:21:52,240
I said, did you tell on us?

256
00:21:52,699 --> 00:21:54,499
No.

257
00:21:55,040 --> 00:21:57,160
If it's not you, who could it be?

258
00:21:57,160 --> 00:21:59,400
Why are you such a big mouth?

259
00:22:01,210 --> 00:22:03,599
Watch your mouth.

260
00:22:04,650 --> 00:22:06,459
So what if I don't?

261
00:22:06,459 --> 00:22:07,640
Speak nicely. Don't get physical.

262
00:22:07,640 --> 00:22:09,540
What do you mean speak nicely?

263
00:22:09,540 --> 00:22:11,619
If it wasn't him, who could it be?

264
00:22:11,619 --> 00:22:13,639
I told you it wasn't me!

265
00:22:16,780 --> 00:22:19,480
Lights out! Go to sleep!

266
00:22:20,900 --> 00:22:22,400
Just you wait.

267
00:22:47,730 --> 00:22:49,639
Gao Yang,

268
00:22:49,639 --> 00:22:51,979
there's still some time left in the summer vacation.

269
00:22:51,979 --> 00:22:57,920
Rome wasn't built in a day. You have to alternate work with rest, you know?

270
00:22:58,600 --> 00:23:02,560
I made you a bowl of noodles with two poached eggs to supplement your brain.

271
00:23:06,010 --> 00:23:07,719
What do you mean?

272
00:23:07,719 --> 00:23:11,400
You think my noodles don't taste as good as Xiaowen's?

273
00:23:16,519 --> 00:23:18,499
I see.

274
00:23:18,499 --> 00:23:22,979
Do you want to finish earlier so you can go visit Xiaowen?

275
00:23:22,979 --> 00:23:25,100
You don't know anything.

276
00:23:25,580 --> 00:23:27,460
Don't forget to eat the noodles.

277
00:24:07,580 --> 00:24:10,320
Xiao... Xiaowen, are you okay?

278
00:24:11,179 --> 00:24:13,860
Why did you push him?

279
00:24:13,860 --> 00:24:15,560
What's wrong?

280
00:24:15,560 --> 00:24:18,359
Nothing, Coach. I just fell.

281
00:24:18,359 --> 00:24:21,339
- Be careful.
- He pushed you deliberately.

282
00:24:22,060 --> 00:24:25,060
Mr. Gao made a lot of effort to get me this opportunity.

283
00:24:25,979 --> 00:24:27,679
Forget it.

284
00:24:29,620 --> 00:24:32,700
Where did you get injured? Does it hurt?

285
00:24:32,700 --> 00:24:34,259
I'm fine.

286
00:24:38,970 --> 00:24:41,200
All right, put it here.

287
00:25:22,559 --> 00:25:24,590
Jump down if you dare!

288
00:25:35,100 --> 00:25:36,580
Sizhe,

289
00:25:36,580 --> 00:25:40,000
it's so late and he's still not back. Did something really happen to him?

290
00:25:40,000 --> 00:25:43,059
That's not possible. There's no lack of oxygen.

291
00:25:43,059 --> 00:25:48,059
Besides, that's what he gets for being a snitch. I hate disloyal people like that.

292
00:25:48,059 --> 00:25:50,219
When are we going to release him?

293
00:25:50,219 --> 00:25:53,319
There's no rush. Let him reflect on his actions.

294
00:25:53,780 --> 00:25:58,560
Think about it, if it wasn't for him, would the coach take dorm inspections so seriously?

295
00:26:03,219 --> 00:26:05,540
You really jumped?

296
00:26:06,540 --> 00:26:08,740
Let me reiterate,

297
00:26:08,740 --> 00:26:13,420
I'm here to train. It doesn't matter what you think about me,

298
00:26:13,420 --> 00:26:16,440
but if you affect my training again,

299
00:26:16,440 --> 00:26:19,140
I can just as well tell Coach Zhang.

300
00:26:32,340 --> 00:26:36,280
See?

301
00:26:37,900 --> 00:26:40,820
Gao Yang, talk to me for a while!

302
00:26:40,820 --> 00:26:43,359
No, I'm studying!

303
00:26:53,970 --> 00:26:58,779
Gao Yang, do you want to watch DVDs?

304
00:26:58,779 --> 00:27:00,280
Don't disturb me.

305
00:27:03,200 --> 00:27:10,290
♫  It's right in front of me, waiting for me to shine  ♫

306
00:27:12,860 --> 00:27:14,680
Brother Yang, let's go fishing.

307
00:27:14,680 --> 00:27:16,449
No, I need to study.

308
00:27:16,449 --> 00:27:22,349
♫  Accompanying me on my adventure, packing my dreams in my heart  ♫

309
00:27:22,349 --> 00:27:29,001
♫  I don't fear the rough journey ahead, I will no longer run away  ♫

310
00:27:29,001 --> 00:27:34,641
♫  Maybe I'm not destined for the hardship of this journey  ♫

311
00:27:34,641 --> 00:27:38,654
♫  To chase after the longing in my heart  ♫

312
00:27:38,654 --> 00:27:41,976
♫  Let's set sail on your dreams  ♫

313
00:27:41,976 --> 00:27:45,371
♫  Let's not have any regrets in our youth  ♫

314
00:27:45,371 --> 00:27:52,031
♫  Even if you stumble and fall, I'll be by your side  ♫

315
00:27:52,031 --> 00:27:55,411
♫  Let's find the answer through the madness  ♫

316
00:27:55,411 --> 00:27:59,423
♫  Let's have courage to ride the waves and billows  ♫

317
00:27:59,423 --> 00:28:03,100
♫  With my wings, I'll fly us to the future  ♫

318
00:28:03,100 --> 00:28:10,370
♫  And step forward into the future without fear of sorrow  ♫

319
00:28:25,620 --> 00:28:28,340
Auntie, why are you here? Come in.

320
00:28:28,340 --> 00:28:30,379
Mr. Gao, you're home?

321
00:28:30,379 --> 00:28:35,900
I made some food for Mi Jia and Xiaowen. Can you help me bring it to them?

322
00:28:35,900 --> 00:28:37,680
Okay, no problem. Give me this.

323
00:28:37,680 --> 00:28:38,920
Sorry to trouble you.

324
00:28:38,920 --> 00:28:42,259
Let me do it. Don't worry, Auntie.

325
00:28:42,259 --> 00:28:45,179
Silly child. Come on, Auntie. Take a seat.

326
00:28:45,179 --> 00:28:47,559
Look, I'm always troubling you.

327
00:28:47,559 --> 00:28:49,440
It's okay.

328
00:28:49,839 --> 00:28:51,540
What should I wear?

329
00:28:51,540 --> 00:28:55,820
Mr. Gao, is it okay for Gao Yang to go alone?

330
00:28:55,820 --> 00:29:00,039
Don't worry, Auntie. It's just Linyang. It'll be like visiting a neighbor.

331
00:29:00,039 --> 00:29:01,719
Besides,

332
00:29:02,219 --> 00:29:04,939
Gao Yang has been studying really hard lately.

333
00:29:04,939 --> 00:29:08,259
It will be a short break for him to relax a little.

334
00:29:08,860 --> 00:29:10,700
That's good.

335
00:29:11,499 --> 00:29:13,699
Who is this?

336
00:29:15,340 --> 00:29:16,840
Hello?

337
00:29:19,860 --> 00:29:22,760
The number you've dialed is overdue.

338
00:29:24,690 --> 00:29:27,919
Mr. Gao, what do you mean by that?

339
00:29:27,919 --> 00:29:31,500
Auntie, I've been getting a lot of these nuisance calls.

340
00:29:31,500 --> 00:29:34,100
They're either promoting insurance or health care products.

341
00:29:34,100 --> 00:29:35,419
They're so annoying.

342
00:29:35,419 --> 00:29:39,479
But if you tell them that, they won't call you anymore.

343
00:29:40,459 --> 00:29:42,719
That's a good method.

344
00:29:47,599 --> 00:29:49,099
Here we are.

345
00:29:57,140 --> 00:29:58,940
Thank you, Sir.

346
00:30:00,179 --> 00:30:01,979
G-Gao Yang!

347
00:30:03,759 --> 00:30:05,480
Why did you come out to greet me?

348
00:30:05,480 --> 00:30:07,119
Let me carry it.

349
00:30:07,930 --> 00:30:11,860
What a grand gesture. You came specially to greet me.

350
00:30:11,860 --> 00:30:14,920
Well, Mi Jia,

351
00:30:15,860 --> 00:30:20,560
Auntie brought you insoles, red jujubes, and pork knuckle.

352
00:30:20,560 --> 00:30:23,230
These are all for the two of you. Enjoy them.

353
00:30:23,230 --> 00:30:24,820
[Track and Field Sports School of Liaoning Province]

354
00:30:24,820 --> 00:30:25,780
They are all here?

355
00:30:25,780 --> 00:30:27,359
Yes.

356
00:30:27,359 --> 00:30:28,739
Is there anything else?

357
00:30:28,739 --> 00:30:30,239
No.

358
00:30:31,179 --> 00:30:33,639
Well, go take a cab home.

359
00:30:33,639 --> 00:30:36,100
What do you mean by saying that?

360
00:30:36,100 --> 00:30:38,620
Do... do you have any idea how long it took me to get here?

361
00:30:38,620 --> 00:30:41,580
I haven't eaten yet. You have to at least buy me lunch.

362
00:30:41,580 --> 00:30:45,719
We... we just eat in the cafeteria here. It's not really good.

363
00:30:45,719 --> 00:30:50,359
That's okay. I'm not picky. I'm starving. The cafeteria's ok. Let's go, Mi Jia.

364
00:30:52,140 --> 00:30:55,319
- This is too heavy for you. Let's go.
- It's not heavy.

365
00:30:55,319 --> 00:30:58,319
What do you mean not heavy? It's red jujubes.

366
00:31:07,140 --> 00:31:10,939
Not bad. Better than I imagined.

367
00:31:12,160 --> 00:31:14,379
Which bed is yours?

368
00:31:14,379 --> 00:31:15,900
That one.

369
00:31:21,839 --> 00:31:25,060
Who's hanging their underwear here?
Is it yours?

370
00:31:25,060 --> 00:31:26,760
No.

371
00:31:27,459 --> 00:31:30,879
You already had lunch. It's time to leave.

372
00:31:31,739 --> 00:31:32,939
Wait,

373
00:31:32,939 --> 00:31:35,419
why are you always trying to send me away?

374
00:31:35,419 --> 00:31:38,700
I just had lunch. It was too salty. Get me some water.

375
00:31:39,699 --> 00:31:41,979
Did you finish all the problems I left you?

376
00:31:41,979 --> 00:31:44,940
See? You still don't really know me.

377
00:31:46,699 --> 00:31:48,499
Where are your roommates?

378
00:31:48,499 --> 00:31:51,780
Why don't I see your roommates? How are you getting along with them?

379
00:31:51,780 --> 00:31:53,179
We're all right.

380
00:31:53,179 --> 00:31:55,079
Where are they from?

381
00:31:55,979 --> 00:31:57,579
I don't know.

382
00:31:58,259 --> 00:32:01,419
You don't know? You call that alright?

383
00:32:01,419 --> 00:32:05,540
Why haven't you learned how to conduct yourself from me?

384
00:32:07,759 --> 00:32:10,400
I'm here to train. Why should I ask about that?

385
00:32:10,400 --> 00:32:12,820
That's your mistake then.

386
00:32:12,820 --> 00:32:15,140
When you see someone, don't you have to get to know them?

387
00:32:15,140 --> 00:32:17,740
If you keep staying quiet, people will misunderstand you.

388
00:32:21,780 --> 00:32:23,280
By the way,

389
00:32:24,979 --> 00:32:29,000
does anyone have a problem with you? I'll help you talk to them.

390
00:32:29,979 --> 00:32:31,359
No.

391
00:32:31,359 --> 00:32:34,820
It's better early than late to catch the train. You should leave now.

392
00:32:36,510 --> 00:32:37,540
Go.

393
00:32:37,540 --> 00:32:40,280
- Wait a minute.
- What now?

394
00:32:40,280 --> 00:32:41,739
What's happened?

395
00:32:41,739 --> 00:32:45,540
It's normal to get hurt during training. Go, go. Go home now.

396
00:32:45,540 --> 00:32:48,920
All right, fine. Give that to me. I'll carry them myself.

397
00:32:48,920 --> 00:32:51,999
Focus on your training. I'm leaving.

398
00:32:53,340 --> 00:32:55,340
Stay safe.

399
00:32:55,340 --> 00:32:57,300
I'm leaving.

400
00:33:27,900 --> 00:33:30,699
Hello, you're getting hot water? Can you pour me a glass?

401
00:33:30,699 --> 00:33:31,739
Sure.

402
00:33:31,739 --> 00:33:33,739
Thank you.

403
00:33:33,739 --> 00:33:34,900
Are you new here?

404
00:33:34,900 --> 00:33:36,900
Yes, I'm new.

405
00:33:36,900 --> 00:33:38,240
Which floor are you staying on?

406
00:33:38,240 --> 00:33:39,940
I'm on the third floor.

407
00:33:39,940 --> 00:33:43,819
The third floor? Are you in the same room as Ye Xiaowen?

408
00:33:43,819 --> 00:33:46,280
No. I live next door to them.

409
00:33:46,280 --> 00:33:49,839
Do you know him very well? I'll be in the same group as him tomorrow.

410
00:33:49,839 --> 00:33:54,780
I don't know him very well, but his roommates don't really like him.

411
00:33:54,780 --> 00:33:56,480
Why?

412
00:33:56,480 --> 00:33:58,879
Chen Sizhe had a conflict with him.

413
00:34:01,000 --> 00:34:03,739
He said he was a snitch and he came in through connections.

414
00:34:03,739 --> 00:34:06,100
Chen Sizhe? The one from Tieyuan?

415
00:34:06,100 --> 00:34:07,600
That's right.

416
00:34:08,450 --> 00:34:10,780
- Thank you.
- Okay.

417
00:34:11,339 --> 00:34:13,039
Excuse me,

418
00:34:14,300 --> 00:34:18,139
I just remembered the coach asked him to go to the equipment room.

419
00:34:18,139 --> 00:34:19,859
Please go tell him for me.

420
00:34:19,859 --> 00:34:21,859
Sure, no problem.

421
00:34:54,340 --> 00:34:56,379
Coach, you're looking for me?

422
00:34:56,939 --> 00:34:58,539
Coach.

423
00:35:01,139 --> 00:35:03,039
Why isn't he here?

424
00:35:10,539 --> 00:35:12,439
Who are you?

425
00:35:12,439 --> 00:35:14,400
You don't need to know.

426
00:35:16,610 --> 00:35:19,419
You're Chen Sizhe, right?

427
00:35:20,139 --> 00:35:21,880
Do I know you?

428
00:35:21,880 --> 00:35:24,039
You don't need to know.

429
00:35:25,260 --> 00:35:26,780
Student,

430
00:35:26,780 --> 00:35:28,519
let me give you a piece of advice.

431
00:35:28,519 --> 00:35:30,979
You should be nice to your teammates, understand?

432
00:35:30,979 --> 00:35:32,879
What the hell?

433
00:35:34,419 --> 00:35:38,419
Oh, I see. Ye Xiaowen asked you to come, right?

434
00:35:38,419 --> 00:35:40,619
Why do you care?

435
00:35:41,960 --> 00:35:45,700
I knew he was a snitch. Such a wimp.

436
00:35:45,700 --> 00:35:47,800
He's asking for a beating?

437
00:35:47,800 --> 00:35:51,579
Who are you going to beat up? Come on, try me!

438
00:35:51,579 --> 00:35:53,199
What do you want?

439
00:35:53,199 --> 00:35:54,919
- Come on.
- What are you doing?

440
00:35:54,919 --> 00:35:57,019
Watch this!

441
00:36:02,860 --> 00:36:05,960
Do you see that? It doesn't hurt.

442
00:36:08,740 --> 00:36:11,619
Watch this.

443
00:36:15,970 --> 00:36:17,979
That doesn't hurt either.

444
00:36:17,979 --> 00:36:20,440
You little bastard,

445
00:36:22,340 --> 00:36:24,400
I'll smack you!

446
00:36:24,400 --> 00:36:26,200
I don't believe it!

447
00:36:32,490 --> 00:36:35,159
Come on!

448
00:36:36,260 --> 00:36:40,020
Come on!

449
00:36:41,610 --> 00:36:43,819
What else?

450
00:36:47,780 --> 00:36:49,820
You're bleeding.

451
00:36:56,199 --> 00:36:59,279
Even so, it still doesn't hurt.

452
00:37:28,585 --> 00:37:34,433
♫  I know the direction of dawn  ♫

453
00:37:34,433 --> 00:37:41,898
♫  It's right in front of me, waiting for me to shine  ♫

454
00:37:41,898 --> 00:37:47,888
♫  The starlight that shines alone the way  ♫

455
00:37:47,888 --> 00:37:53,928
♫  Accompanying me on my adventure, packing my dreams in my heart  ♫

456
00:37:53,928 --> 00:38:00,580
♫  I don't fear the rough journey ahead, I will no longer run away  ♫

457
00:38:00,580 --> 00:38:06,220
♫  Maybe I'm not destined for the hardship of this journey  ♫

458
00:38:06,220 --> 00:38:10,233
♫  To chase after the longing in my heart  ♫

459
00:38:10,233 --> 00:38:13,655
♫  Let's set sail on your dreams  ♫

460
00:38:13,655 --> 00:38:16,950
♫  Let's not have any regrets in our youth  ♫

461
00:38:16,950 --> 00:38:23,610
♫  Even if you stumble and fall, I'll be by your side  ♫

462
00:38:23,610 --> 00:38:26,921
♫  Let's find the answer through the madness  ♫

463
00:38:26,921 --> 00:38:31,040
♫  Let's have courage to ride the waves and billows  ♫

464
00:38:31,040 --> 00:38:34,953
♫  With my wings, I'll fly us to the future  ♫

465
00:38:34,953 --> 00:38:42,813
♫  And step forward into the future without fear of sorrow  ♫
